==English==
====Etymology====
From [[radius|radi(us)]] + -an

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-reg}}

#{{geometry}} a measure of angle equal to the angle [[subtend]]ed at the [[centre]] of a [[circle]] by an [[arc]] of its [[circumference]] equal in length to the [[radius]] of the circle. Symbol: '''rad'''

